{
  "event_id": "xiaoman_h3",
  "npc_id": "xiaoman",
  "title": "丰收夜的烟火",
  "description": "与小满在丰穰祭夜晚的温馨时刻",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_start",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]！你看你看，烟火好漂亮！这是我第一次这么近看烟火！",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_1",
          "text": "你好像特别开心",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_2",
          "text": "小心别挤到别人了",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_warn"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_happy",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "当然开心啦！丰收的粮食变成美酒，美酒换来烟火。这样的夜晚，一年只有一次呀！",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_agree",
          "text": "和你一起看更开心",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_together"
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_curious",
          "text": "小满家乡的丰收节也这样吗？",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_hometown"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_warn",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "啊……对不起对不起！我太激动了。但是你看那颗蓝色的，像不像云海的颜色？",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_blue",
          "text": "确实像，是今晚最亮的一颗",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_romantic"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_hometown",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "我家乡的丰收节……没有这么热闹。大家就是围在一起吃饭，然后各自回家睡觉。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_miss",
          "text": "会想家吗？",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_nostalgia"
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_comfort",
          "text": "这里也是你的家",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_home"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_nostalgia",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "……有时候会。特别是吃到自己种的稻米的时候，会想起妈妈做的饭。但是云海山庄也很好啊，有大家陪我。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_comfort2",
          "text": "以后有我陪你",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_home"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_home",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]……谢谢你。从我来到山庄，你是第一个对我说这种话的人。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_smile",
          "text": "这是真心话",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_together"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_together",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "快看！又一颗金色的！$[PLAYER_NAME]，我们来许愿吧！听说烟火许愿很灵的！",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_wish",
          "text": "好，一起许愿",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_wish_scene"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_romantic",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "真的吗？……$[PLAYER_NAME]，你知道吗，你站在烟火前面的时候，比那颗蓝色的还亮。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_blush",
          "text": "（脸红了）",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_wish_scene"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_wish_scene",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "好了！我许好了！你许的什么愿望呀？……啊，不对，说出来就不灵了！",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_secret",
          "text": "愿望藏在心里就好",
          "next_node_id": "xiaoman_h3_end"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "xiaoman_h3_end",
      "speaker": "小满",
      "text": "嗯！$[PLAYER_NAME]，今年的丰穰祭是我过得最开心的一次。以后的每年，我们一起来看烟火好不好？",
      "is_ending": true,
      "reward_favor": 25,
      "reward_items": [
        {
          "item_id": "firework_shard",
          "count": 5,
          "description": "烟火碎片 - 丰穰祭的纪念"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
